:INFO
Open Source SaaS Roadmap Planning
A framework for planning and communicating the product roadmap for an open source SaaS product across community and commercial priorities.

:TASK
[ ] Define quarterly themes tied to user and community feedback
[ ] Separate community roadmap from internal commercial roadmap
[ ] Tag every GitHub issue with milestone and priority label
[ ] Run quarterly community vote on top feature requests
[ ] Publish public changelog on every release
[ ] Schedule monthly roadmap update post in community forum
[ ] Review competitor open source projects quarterly
[ ] Assess open core boundary and adjust based on conversion data

:NOTE
Keep the public roadmap honest. Overpromising on timelines destroys community trust faster than shipping slowly. A realistic public roadmap with consistent delivery builds far more goodwill than optimistic timelines you miss.